{"tid":2413753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葵涌消防局多2人確診 1人屬頂更原駐守荔景 140同袍要檢疫","createTime":"2021-02-19T02:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T02:50:01.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bd48e1c494a0562c5342cd7d8d0ef1a52374a68d","tid":2413753,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T02:50:01.000Z","msg":"葵涌消防局爆發武漢肺炎疫情，日前已有2名消防員及1名密切接觸者確診，同時亦有其他消防員及其家人初步確診，衞生防護中心宣佈將該局納入強檢名單。消防處回覆《蘋果》時證實，周四（18日）再多2名消防員證實確診，其中一人駐守葵涌消防局，與早前確診的2人同隊；另一人則駐守荔景消防局，但2月初曾到葵涌消防局「頂更」，連帶同局的140多名消防處人員被列為密切接觸者，需要接受檢疫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/46IPI7NWAZGZHKEPO5Z7U6XWAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2F46IPI7NWAZGZHKEPO5Z7U6XWAI%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Isqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=e829678f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2F46IPI7NWAZGZHKEPO5Z7U6XWAI%2F&h=bb66d135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/46IPI7NWAZGZHKEPO5Z7U6XWAI/</a>"}]}